{"data":[{"name":"2024-02-23 10:16:01","id":1708654561786,"body":"这个题目chatgpt给的思路，如果碰到这种遍历，考虑不同长度的问题，其实可以while里面写||\r\nclass Solution {\r\npublic:\r\n    ListNode* addTwoNumbers(ListNode* l1, ListNode* l2) {\r\n        ListNode* res = new ListNode(0);\r\n        ListNode* ptr = res;\r\n        ListNode* first = l1;\r\n        ListNode* second = l2;\r\n        int carry = 0;\r\n        while (first != nullptr || second != nullptr) {\r\n            int sum = carry;\r\n            if (first != nullptr) {\r\n                sum += first->val;\r\n                first = first->next;\r\n            }\r\n            if (second != nullptr) {\r\n                sum += second->val;\r\n                second = second->next;\r\n            }\r\n            ptr->next = new ListNode(sum % 10);\r\n            carry = sum / 10;\r\n            ptr = ptr->next;\r\n        }\r\n        if (carry != 0) {\r\n            ptr->next = new ListNode(carry);\r\n        }\r\n        return res->next;\r\n    }\r\n};"}]}